title: Nasus with Trinity Force and Frozen Heart asked for blue
body:
I said, "No, I need it," and pinged him back. I had used smite for the stun and mana (because I was oom) already. Nasus Walked up and Q'd it.

I said, "Seriously? I helped you get 3 of those 5 kills. AFK until next blue."

2:30 remaining until it's 5v5 again.
